233
00:19:54,898 --> 00:19:57,567
Sudah tahu akan tertangkap,
kenapa mengulur waktu?

234
00:19:59,611 --> 00:20:00,945
Jo Tae-sik.

235
00:20:01,529 --> 00:20:04,449
Kau mengaku telah membunuh
Kopral Jeon Ho-gyu di tanah kosong

236
00:20:05,241 --> 00:20:07,035
tanggal 8 Mei pukul 22.00?

237
00:20:08,244 --> 00:20:09,370
Kau

238
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:11,289
mengakuinya?

239
00:20:13,875 --> 00:20:17,045
Ada pesan teks darimu hari itu,
pistolmu ditemukan di TKP,

240
00:20:17,796 --> 00:20:20,590
dan pernyataan para inspektur
yang menyaksikanmu kabur.

241
00:20:22,092 --> 00:20:23,718
Akuilah.

242
00:20:24,552 --> 00:20:26,137
Apa pun yang kukatakan,

243
00:20:27,555 --> 00:20:29,349
bukankah jawabannya sudah ada?

244
00:20:30,225 --> 00:20:32,143
Terserah kau mau apa.

245
00:20:32,727 --> 00:20:33,728
Namun,

246
00:20:35,522 --> 00:20:36,689
aku tak akan pernah

247
00:20:38,566 --> 00:20:39,651
mengaku.

248
00:20:40,401 --> 00:20:41,277
Kenapa?

249
00:20:43,113 --> 00:20:44,531
Karena aku tak membunuh Ho-gyu.

250
00:20:45,698 --> 00:20:46,783
Jo Tae-sik!

251
00:20:53,373 --> 00:20:57,210
<i>Bukankah Ayah Mertua, Pak In,
dan Yeong-min di pihak yang sama?</i>

252
00:20:58,670 --> 00:21:01,297
<i>Namun, dari kata-kata Yeong-min,
sepertinya tidak.</i>

253
00:21:02,257 --> 00:21:03,633
<i>Sepertinya Yeong-min</i>

254
00:21:04,968 --> 00:21:07,178
<i>memakai peluang ini
untuk menguasai perusahaan.</i>

255
00:21:09,264 --> 00:21:11,808
<i>Tampaknya tak berkaitan
dengan Sang-hun juga.</i>

256
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:14,686
<i>Ada apa sebenarnya?</i>

257
00:21:16,521 --> 00:21:19,107
DETEKTIF KANG JIN-GYEONG

258
00:21:20,900 --> 00:21:23,236
- Halo, Detektif Kang.
- Bu Kim.

259
00:21:25,780 --> 00:21:28,116
Tae-sik tertangkap.

260
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:31,703
Tertangkap?

261
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:39,711
- Kita harus bagaimana?
- Dia ditahan,

262
00:21:41,045 --> 00:21:42,422
tapi ada alasan.

263
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:46,801
Masalahnya...

264
00:21:54,058 --> 00:21:57,645
Keras kepala sekali. Dia bergeming.

265
00:21:58,605 --> 00:22:01,733
Kita harus bagaimana? Sudah berjam-jam.

266
00:22:03,026 --> 00:22:04,068
Tak akan lama.

267
00:22:12,994 --> 00:22:15,413
Kita punya bukti dan saksi.

268
00:22:16,581 --> 00:22:18,374
Dia bisa didakwa hari ini atau besok.

269
00:22:19,709 --> 00:22:20,877
Sudah cukup?

270
00:22:22,462 --> 00:22:23,755
Sesuai perintahmu,

271
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:26,633
kufitnah Tae-sik atas pembunuhan
dan menahannya.

272
00:22:27,467 --> 00:22:28,635
Tak bisakah ini berakhir?

273
00:22:29,552 --> 00:22:30,637
Kau membunuh

274
00:22:31,763 --> 00:22:33,473
Choe Su-hyeon dan Kim Seung-cheol,

275
00:22:34,432 --> 00:22:35,683
tapi aku menutupinya.

276
00:22:36,851 --> 00:22:38,561
Kututupi Kim Pil-yeon, Choi Chi-deuk,

277
00:22:39,187 --> 00:22:40,563
bahkan kecelakaan Kim Seo-hui.

278
00:22:41,147 --> 00:22:42,315
Karena dirimu,

279
00:22:45,568 --> 00:22:48,321
aku bahkan terpaksa membunuh Ho-gyu.

280
00:22:50,490 --> 00:22:51,783
Tae-sik pun kutahan.

281
00:22:53,785 --> 00:22:55,078
Sudah cukup yang kulakukan.

282
00:22:57,246 --> 00:22:59,290
Membantumu membunuh dan merekayasa kasus.

283
00:23:01,376 --> 00:23:02,502
Aku sudah muak.

284
00:23:03,461 --> 00:23:06,214
Jadi, kembalikan video itu padaku.

285
00:23:08,466 --> 00:23:10,134
Berhenti menekanku.

286
00:23:13,721 --> 00:23:14,764
Baik.

287
00:23:37,912 --> 00:23:39,414
MEREKAM

288
00:23:40,415 --> 00:23:43,584
Pantas saja kau banyak bicara.

289
00:23:47,588 --> 00:23:48,715
Kau tahu?

290
00:23:50,508 --> 00:23:51,592
Aku benci

291
00:23:54,053 --> 00:23:56,431
mengulangi kata-kata yang sama.

292
00:23:58,016 --> 00:24:01,394
Kusuruh kau mengurus Jo Tae-sik.

293
00:24:02,395 --> 00:24:03,813
Setelah dia tersingkir,

294
00:24:05,106 --> 00:24:09,444
kuakhiri semua sesuai keinginanmu.
Sudah kubilang, bukan?

295
00:24:11,571 --> 00:24:12,655
Namun, kenapa...

296
00:24:17,869 --> 00:24:18,953
kau begini?

297
00:24:24,125 --> 00:24:25,460
Katakan sesuatu.

298
00:24:38,556 --> 00:24:40,141
BADAN FORENSIK NASIONAL

299
00:24:44,979 --> 00:24:46,898
- Tae-sik.
- Hei.

300
00:24:48,107 --> 00:24:49,650
HASIL TES

301
00:24:51,069 --> 00:24:53,196
Ditemukan darah Ho-gyu di sepatu Kapten.

302
00:24:53,988 --> 00:24:56,449
Serat di kuku Ho-gyu cocok
dengan baju Kapten.

303
00:24:56,532 --> 00:24:57,950
Akhirnya.

304
00:24:58,034 --> 00:25:00,119
Kau bisa buktikan kau tak bersalah.

305
00:25:00,203 --> 00:25:01,704
Kita bisa menangkap Kapten Yu.

306
00:25:02,205 --> 00:25:03,831
Ayo tahan dia.

307
00:25:05,208 --> 00:25:06,167
Tunggu.

308
00:25:06,793 --> 00:25:08,419
Jika menangkap Dae-yong sekarang,

309
00:25:08,836 --> 00:25:11,756
In Dong-gu akan langsung tahu,
lalu akan berbuat apa?

310
00:25:12,340 --> 00:25:15,426
Dia akan menjebak Dae-yong
dan kabur ke luar negeri.

311
00:25:15,927 --> 00:25:16,969
Kemudian...

312
00:25:17,804 --> 00:25:20,389
Dae-yong menanggung kesalahan,
kita kehilangan dalangnya.

313
00:25:20,681 --> 00:25:23,601
Lantas, kita harus bagaimana?

314
00:25:24,393 --> 00:25:25,561
Saat ini,

315
00:25:26,521 --> 00:25:29,232
Dae-yong pasti tahu kau mengambil bajunya.

316
00:25:30,358 --> 00:25:32,527
Aku harus menemuinya.

317
00:25:57,093 --> 00:25:59,053
Kau mencuci bajumu untuk berjaga-jaga.

318
00:26:00,012 --> 00:26:02,723
Namun, tak tahu darah Ho-gyu di sepatumu.

319
00:26:04,559 --> 00:26:06,644
Serat yang ditemukan di kuku Ho-gyu cocok

320
00:26:06,727 --> 00:26:08,396
dengan serat bajumu.

321
00:26:09,605 --> 00:26:11,399
Jin-gyeong sudah menemui inspektur

322
00:26:11,732 --> 00:26:14,443
dengan membawa hasil tes
dan riwayat panggilan teleponmu.

323
00:26:14,819 --> 00:26:15,945
Dengan semua itu,

324
00:26:16,946 --> 00:26:19,323
dia bisa buktikan
kau di sana saat Ho-gyu tewas,

325
00:26:19,574 --> 00:26:22,493
dan membunuhnya setelah berkelahi.

326
00:26:25,079 --> 00:26:26,455
Sudah berakhir, Dae-yong.

327
00:26:28,833 --> 00:26:29,876
Selesai.

328
00:26:30,710 --> 00:26:31,711
Jadi...

329
00:26:32,837 --> 00:26:34,380
Kenapa kau di sini?

330
00:26:35,548 --> 00:26:38,176
Kau datang untuk menyuruhku
bersiap-siap ditangkap?

331
00:26:40,219 --> 00:26:41,679
Apa maumu?

332
00:26:42,805 --> 00:26:44,348
Kenapa tak menahanku tempo hari?

333
00:26:44,932 --> 00:26:46,392
- Apa?
- Saat aku buron

334
00:26:46,475 --> 00:26:49,187
dan pergi ke tempatmu,
kau bisa menangkapku.

335
00:26:50,062 --> 00:26:51,856
Bahkan bisa membunuhku jika mau.

336
00:26:54,775 --> 00:26:55,735
Kau tak bermaksud

337
00:26:56,611 --> 00:26:58,362
membunuh Ho-gyu, bukan?

338
00:27:01,032 --> 00:27:03,201
Kau pun tak berniat memfitnahku.

339
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:07,288
Jika demikian,
kau akan bawa pistolku sejak awal.

340
00:27:08,623 --> 00:27:10,291
Namun, kau mencuri pistolku

341
00:27:11,876 --> 00:27:13,252
setelah Ho-gyu tewas.

342
00:27:17,256 --> 00:27:18,341
Dae-yong.

343
00:27:19,842 --> 00:27:20,676
Aku kenal kau.

344
00:27:22,887 --> 00:27:24,388
Apa alasanmu?

345
00:27:26,057 --> 00:27:29,268
Bagaimana In Dong-gu
bisa menekanmu begini?

346
00:27:30,353 --> 00:27:31,395
Kenapa bertanya?

347
00:27:32,271 --> 00:27:33,314
Jika tahu,

348
00:27:34,023 --> 00:27:36,651
kau mau bunuh In Dong-gu untukku?

349
00:27:38,319 --> 00:27:39,445
Aku bisa.

350
00:27:40,988 --> 00:27:42,281
Akan kubunuh dia.

351
00:27:43,366 --> 00:27:46,077
Jika hanya dengan cara itu
kau bisa bebas darinya,

352
00:27:47,870 --> 00:27:49,080
akan kubunuh dia demimu.

353
00:27:50,998 --> 00:27:52,541
Jadi, serahkan dirimu, Dae-yong.

354
00:27:54,627 --> 00:27:56,420
Menyerahlah, bantu tangkap In Dong-gu.

355
00:27:58,464 --> 00:28:00,716
Hanya itu cara menebus dosamu.

356
00:28:03,010 --> 00:28:05,805
Satu-satunya cara menyingkirkan
In Dong-gu, bajingan itu.

357
00:28:08,140 --> 00:28:09,100
Dae-yong.

358
00:29:09,660 --> 00:29:11,329
Lepaskan dia, Berengsek!

359
00:29:11,495 --> 00:29:12,705
Hentikan, Dae-yong.

360
00:29:14,248 --> 00:29:15,499
Jangan tembak.

361
00:29:16,250 --> 00:29:17,418
Jangan!

362
00:29:19,211 --> 00:29:20,338
Dae-yong, hentikan!

363
00:29:21,213 --> 00:29:22,840
Tidak, Dae-yong.

364
00:29:25,343 --> 00:29:26,469
Hei.

365
00:29:30,181 --> 00:29:31,515
Apa? Itu pistol?

366
00:29:31,599 --> 00:29:33,434
Pergi. Nyalakan mobil.

367
00:29:44,403 --> 00:29:46,238
Tamatlah riwayatmu.

368
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:50,701
- In Dong-gu!
- Belum selesai.

369
00:29:50,785 --> 00:29:52,119
Tae-sik.

370
00:29:53,287 --> 00:29:54,288
Berikan padaku.

371
00:29:56,290 --> 00:29:58,376
In Dong-gu, lepaskan dia, angkat tangan.

372
00:30:01,504 --> 00:30:02,797
Angkat tangan, Keparat!

373
00:30:15,810 --> 00:30:18,771
Kau ingin aku membuat In Dong-gu
mengakui perbuatannya?

374
00:30:19,438 --> 00:30:20,773
Kenal dia, bukan?

375
00:30:22,358 --> 00:30:23,984
Dia pasti akan tahu.

376
00:30:24,068 --> 00:30:25,695
Jika itu sebagian rencana kita?

377
00:30:28,447 --> 00:30:31,534
Ini tempat pertemuan In Dong-gu
dan Kapten Yu.

378
00:30:32,034 --> 00:30:35,162
Kapten Yu akan menemui In Dong-gu
dengan penyadap di bajunya.

379
00:30:35,371 --> 00:30:37,373
Kita akan memantau dari jauh.

380
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:40,418
Setelah In Dong-gu mengatakan hal penting,

381
00:30:41,335 --> 00:30:42,503
kepung dia.

382
00:30:42,586 --> 00:30:43,671
- Baik.
- Baik.

383
00:30:51,887 --> 00:30:53,347
Tae-sik.

384
00:31:04,150 --> 00:31:06,193
Kusuruh kau mengurus Jo Tae-sik.

385
00:31:06,986 --> 00:31:08,404
Setelah dia tersingkir,

386
00:31:08,988 --> 00:31:10,865
<i>kuakhiri semua sesuai keinginanmu.</i>

387
00:31:12,032 --> 00:31:15,119
<i>Sudah kubilang, bukan?</i>

388
00:31:19,832 --> 00:31:21,250
In Dong-gu.

389
00:31:22,084 --> 00:31:23,377
Kau ditahan

390
00:31:24,253 --> 00:31:25,963
atas pembunuhan

391
00:31:26,547 --> 00:31:28,299
Choe Su-hyeon, Kim Seung-cheol,

392
00:31:28,799 --> 00:31:30,718
Choi Chi-deuk, dan Kim Pil-yeon.

393
00:31:36,265 --> 00:31:38,559
Kau berhak memanggil pengacara

394
00:31:40,060 --> 00:31:41,604
dan membela diri...

395
00:31:44,940 --> 00:31:45,941
Lupakan.

396
00:31:47,902 --> 00:31:49,153
Kau sudah tahu.

397
00:31:50,321 --> 00:31:52,406
Kau profesional sejati.

398
00:31:53,073 --> 00:31:54,283
Hei.

399
00:31:54,366 --> 00:31:55,367
Ini.

400
00:31:56,702 --> 00:31:57,703
Bawa dia.

401
00:32:13,844 --> 00:32:15,054
Hei, Kang Jin-gyeong.

402
00:32:16,514 --> 00:32:17,348
Borgol aku.

403
00:32:32,196 --> 00:32:33,239
Ayo pergi.

404
00:32:38,077 --> 00:32:39,662
Dalam situasi ini,

405
00:32:39,745 --> 00:32:42,498
Pak In tak bisa dibebaskan.

406
00:32:43,332 --> 00:32:44,917
Komisaris Jenderal Pak.

407
00:32:45,751 --> 00:32:47,002
Kau tak bisa bantu?

408
00:32:47,086 --> 00:32:48,504
<i>Mohon maaf, Pak.</i>

409
00:32:48,587 --> 00:32:50,923
Dengan bukti sekuat itu,

410
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:53,884
tak mungkin bisa ditutupi.

411
00:32:57,137 --> 00:32:58,472
Ada yang salah.

412
00:33:00,516 --> 00:33:01,892
Pasti ada yang tak beres.

413
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:06,105
Jika tidak, kenapa kita
terus menghadapi masalah?

414
00:33:06,230 --> 00:33:09,024
Pak, utamakan masalah darurat.

415
00:33:09,650 --> 00:33:11,819
Kita tak bisa berbuat apa pun saat ini.

416
00:33:13,237 --> 00:33:15,489
Singkirkan Pak In.

417
00:33:22,538 --> 00:33:24,290
Sejak kapan?

418
00:33:26,417 --> 00:33:27,960
Sejak kapan kau terlibat

419
00:33:28,961 --> 00:33:30,045
dengan In Dong-gu?

420
00:33:32,172 --> 00:33:35,259
<i>Min-cheol, kau sungguh berniat
melaporkanku ke jaksa?</i>

421
00:33:35,342 --> 00:33:38,053
Kau sering menerima suap
dan melepaskan mereka.

422
00:33:38,137 --> 00:33:40,097
Kau pikir siapa kau?

423
00:33:40,180 --> 00:33:42,850
- Kau sendiri bersih?
- Ya, tanganku bersih.

424
00:33:42,933 --> 00:33:44,852
<i>Ada perampokan bersenjata di Yangjae-dong.</i>

425
00:33:44,935 --> 00:33:47,313
<i>Tersangka buron. Kami butuh bantuan.</i>

426
00:33:47,396 --> 00:33:48,647
Kau tidak mau kerja?

427
00:33:48,731 --> 00:33:50,190
Sial!

428
00:33:55,279 --> 00:33:56,155
Jatuhkan pisaumu!

429
00:34:00,618 --> 00:34:02,286
Bajingan!

430
00:34:06,957 --> 00:34:08,042
Bajingan!

431
00:34:11,503 --> 00:34:12,630
Dae-yong...

432
00:34:15,633 --> 00:34:18,552
<i>Aku ingin menolongnya,</i>

433
00:34:20,137 --> 00:34:23,098
<i>tapi entah kenapa, kakiku tertahan.</i>

434
00:34:29,897 --> 00:34:31,273
<i>Jika dia lenyap...</i>

435
00:34:32,358 --> 00:34:33,776
<i>Jika kuabaikan hal itu,</i>

436
00:34:35,277 --> 00:34:36,862
<i>kukira semua akan beres.</i>

437
00:34:38,113 --> 00:34:39,114
Tak apa-apa.

438
00:34:39,740 --> 00:34:41,075
Dae-yong...

439
00:34:45,329 --> 00:34:46,330
Tak apa-apa.

440
00:34:47,164 --> 00:34:48,999
<i>Pikiranku sedang kacau.</i>

441
00:34:57,883 --> 00:35:00,636
Aku bersusah payah menemukan ini.

442
00:35:02,471 --> 00:35:04,223
- Kau...
- Tugasnya tak banyak.

443
00:35:09,520 --> 00:35:10,938
Kau hanya perlu

444
00:35:11,563 --> 00:35:13,440
merekayasa satu kasus.

445
00:35:15,484 --> 00:35:19,822
Kau mengancam Yu Dae-yong,
dengan pembunuhan

446
00:35:19,905 --> 00:35:22,449
Detektif Park Min-cheol
sepuluh tahun lalu.

447
00:35:24,410 --> 00:35:27,079
Tanggal 14 Februari,
kau pergi ke rumah Choe Su-hyeon,

448
00:35:27,162 --> 00:35:29,164
memberinya obat,
dan mendorongnya dari atap.

449
00:35:29,248 --> 00:35:31,125
Lalu kau mengancam Kapten Yu

450
00:35:31,667 --> 00:35:33,836
agar kasus itu dinyatakan bunuh diri.

451
00:35:34,753 --> 00:35:35,963
Kau mengakuinya?

452
00:35:38,048 --> 00:35:40,384
Bagaimana dengan kecelakaan
Kim Seung-cheol?

453
00:35:43,095 --> 00:35:45,014
Itu perbuatanmu.

454
00:35:46,015 --> 00:35:47,016
Benar?

455
00:37:04,968 --> 00:37:06,261
Jadi...

456
00:37:07,387 --> 00:37:10,682
kau yang menghancurkan
mobil Kim Seung-cheol?

457
00:37:12,101 --> 00:37:13,727
In Dong-gu menyuruhmu?

458
00:37:18,649 --> 00:37:19,942
Pergilah.

459
00:37:24,738 --> 00:37:27,074
Kematian Kim Pil-yeon dan Choi Chi-deuk?

460
00:37:28,534 --> 00:37:31,620
Kau menghubungi In Dong-gu
tepat sebelum mereka tewas.

461
00:37:34,790 --> 00:37:36,125
- Kapten Yu.
- Ya?

462
00:37:36,208 --> 00:37:39,378
Kim Seo-hui sedang menuju Pelabuhan Ansan.

463
00:37:40,546 --> 00:37:41,922
Kau yakin?

464
00:37:42,005 --> 00:37:43,507
- Ya.
- Baik.

465
00:37:48,470 --> 00:37:49,388
Ya, Detektif.

466
00:37:50,013 --> 00:37:52,391
Tampaknya Kim Seo-hui
menuju Pelabuhan Ansan.

467
00:38:06,864 --> 00:38:09,783
Kurasa bajingan itu bohong.

468
00:38:10,284 --> 00:38:11,535
Keadaan di rumah sakit?

469
00:38:11,618 --> 00:38:12,953
Tahu siapa yang ada di sana?

470
00:38:13,036 --> 00:38:14,580
Kuperiksa sekarang.

471
00:38:16,748 --> 00:38:18,667
PAK IN

472
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:23,297
CHOI CHI-DEUK SEDANG SENDIRIAN

473
